{"id":136304,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/02/简讯：中国农业部下令严查“皮革奶”/","date":"2011-02-16T16:50:48Z","modified":"2011-02-16T16:50:48Z","title":"简讯：中国农业部下令严查“皮革奶”","content":"<div>\n<p>中国农业部近日发出今年安全检测计划文件，要求各地除要检测三聚氰胺外，还要严格检测皮革水解蛋白和碱类物质。</p>\n<p>“皮革水解蛋白”是以废旧皮革制品甚至动物毛发予以“水解”后生成的粉状物质。</p>\n<p>不法奸商将其混入牛奶，用于提高蛋白质含量，长期食用可能会致癌。</p>\n<p>中国媒体引述北京专家说，皮革水解蛋白的检测难度比三聚氰胺还大，因为它本身就是一种蛋白质。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a-ssn4E6v3bF1bF9ZLRGoJQHxtU/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a-ssn4E6v3bF1bF9ZLRGoJQHxtU/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a-ssn4E6v3bF1bF9ZLRGoJQHxtU/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/a-ssn4E6v3bF1bF9ZLRGoJQHxtU/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=seM4OQ8alwg:oR6S06PY9ls:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=seM4OQ8alwg:oR6S06PY9ls:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=seM4OQ8alwg:oR6S06PY9ls:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=seM4OQ8alwg:oR6S06PY9ls:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=seM4OQ8alwg:oR6S06PY9ls:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=seM4OQ8alwg:oR6S06PY9ls:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/seM4OQ8alwg\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>更多翻墙方式请发电邮(最好用Gmail)到:CDTc